snippet.title: Windswept - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Windswept is a '90s-inspired platformer about 2 friends trying to find their way back home.
Jump, spin, flutter and throw yourself into a classic adventure of galactic proportions!

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1660960/Windswept/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WeatherFell
